{"tid":1602803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(香城online）要求所有火魔法師轉職","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:04:40.000Z","uid":323612,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf106b3fc83335edbfe73f874bc1ece71681f63","tid":1602803,"uid":323612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"班狗或狗車對火魔法有抗性，即使掟中狗或狗車身上，傷害都唔大。而家有一種新職業可以同時對狗或狗車造成長時間嘅持續傷害，就係操蟲使。以火影入面嘅油女一族為例，即使敵人有幾重幾厚嘅甲，只要條友副甲有足夠空間比蟲爬入去，佢哋就不攻自破，班狗自然會除低裝備，希望即早解除特殊傷害效果，咁我哋就可以即時趁機擊破。"},{"pid":"1a580237d6241ed5d937bfcf4f200e04d2d76958","tid":1602803,"uid":104811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"f2f0ff0708690108a4d6881348bd94f2645e5b0e","tid":1602803,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"火系保留 但係蟲系出動先"},{"pid":"3fd9c16cade6e41cbe521b7c1315fe78a1e434b0","tid":1602803,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c6789e2eafc6554a47a9b04dda21947f9043eb9","tid":1602803,"uid":323612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2f0ff0708690108a4d6881348bd94f2645e5b0e","tid":1602803,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"火系保留 但係蟲系出動先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"蟲糸對狗有持續傷害，同時可以減低防禦力"},{"pid":"987216f5245578519946bcb06f6e70963e20eab2","tid":1602803,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> why not both"},{"pid":"9d6dcc344318dde8a422a3077580420daa12fc14","tid":1602803,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:04:40.000Z","msg":"我建議大部分由自來也轉做文太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣可以令佢地污糟，一燒槍就火燒連環船"}]}